Uses of Package
org.kiji.rest.representations

Packages that use org.kiji.rest.representations
org.kiji.rest.representations Contains representation classes used for GETting/POSTing resources. 
org.kiji.rest.resources Contains resources that respond to REST requests. 
org.kiji.rest.serializers Contains custom object to JSON serializers. 
org.kiji.rest.util Utility classes for KijiREST. 
 

Classes in org.kiji.rest.representations used by org.kiji.rest.representations
KijiRestCell
          Models what a Kiji cell looks like when returned to the client.
KijiRestEntityId
          Container class for entity ids which can be backed as strings (suitable for raw, hashed, hash-prefixed, and materialization suppressed keys) xor as a list of components (suitable for formatted entity ids without materialization unsuppresed).
SchemaOption
          Class that holds two (mutually exclusive) representations of an Avro schema.
